{"tid":2359733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自設「踏浪者」獎章　鄧炳強頒發嘉許 74 警　表揚反送中行動「勇氣智慧」","createTime":"2021-01-09T06:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T06:16:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":276,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"5c3896304787e7fdc375d7e3eeb9a53bf35a4c0e","tid":2359733,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/popo-02_LMgkQ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpopo-02_LMgkQ_1200x0.png&h=9429de23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警隊官方刊物《警聲》最新一期報道，警方在 12 月 30 日，舉行首場「踏浪者」行動獎章頒授典禮，由警務處處長鄧炳強，頒授印有「蒙面防暴警」圖案的行動獎章，給 74 位在反送中運動有份參與行動的警員，而據警聲的介紹，「踏浪者」行動獎章分別繡上橙色或者紫色橫間，橙色代表「勇氣」、紫色代表「智慧」。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強在頒獎禮上指，警員「要繼續承風破浪」、「暴力與污衊會落幕」，又稱「滄海橫流，方顯英雄本色」，警員為捍衛香港、守護香港市民的「辛勞與犧牲」，會被「國家和香港市民」銘記。<br />\n<br />\n根據《警聲》的「報道」，在參與反修例示威「踏浪者」行動中，面對「前所未見的挑戰」仍秉持「專業精神」，恢復社會「法治和秩序」、面對迫切危險時「表現英勇」、為參與行動的警員提供「卓越」支援服務，就可獲推薦授予「踏浪者」行動獎章。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%87%AA%E8%A8%AD-%E8%B8%8F%E6%B5%AA%E8%80%85-%E7%8D%8E%E7%AB%A0-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E9%A0%92%E7%99%BC%E5%98%89%E8%A8%B1-74-%E8%AD%A6-%E8%A1%A8%E6%8F%9A%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E5%8B%87%E6%B0%A3%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E8%25B8%258F%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E8%2580%2585-%25E7%258D%258E%25E7%25AB%25A0-%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%25A0%2592%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2598%2589%25E8%25A8%25B1-74-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%258F%259A%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=106a192b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E8%25B8%258F%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E8%2580%2585-%25E7%258D%258E%25E7%25AB%25A0-%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%25A0%2592%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2598%2589%25E8%25A8%25B1-74-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%258F%259A%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%2F&h=434b7aaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%87%AA%E8%A8%AD-%E8%B8%8F%E6%B5%AA%E8%80%85-%E7%8D%8E%E7%AB%A0-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E9%A0%92%E7%99%BC%E5%98%89%E8%A8%B1-74-%E8%AD%A6-%E8%A1%A8%E6%8F%9A%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E5%8B%87%E6%B0%A3%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/</a>"},{"pid":"90e4b7ebb5a0094af2d2b5267a746d06b478d540","tid":2359733,"uid":58685,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"豬肉獎"},{"pid":"b3bd726142d23277ff775c260da312b7af0fe76a","tid":2359733,"uid":36722,"like":163,"dislike":2,"score":161,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944c5f3adeb6a6a3364e367fd9e4cb14ce2a53d1","tid":2359733,"uid":23635,"like":231,"dislike":1,"score":230,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v2YkNFm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv2YkNFm.png&h=e9999544&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82e3c4e4f8028e21ca866cfb229991a23dcd174a","tid":2359733,"uid":94177,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"名單呢？<br />\nd獎比左邊個呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82021b1bf506eb7ae8343faaa1c768779f4f2763","tid":2359733,"uid":6810,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"勇氣都算<br />\n智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4e5d5a2579a9739a757f